{"tid":2178641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個on9 Miss/阿Sir","createTime":"2020-08-28T13:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T14:10:05.000Z","uid":290804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a13669b8aba6a9813f99af2a177b91f3bb9a84bb","tid":2178641,"uid":290804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"中學英文堂miss喺黑板寫緊嘢 後面有人㩒咗幾下原子筆 點知佢即時發癲 問邊個玩筆 全班冇人應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靜咗5分鐘之後 繼續上堂 之後我唔覺意手痕㩒咗幾下<br />\n佢即刻擰轉頭拍檯 話今日唔上堂喇......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家霖翻起 其實佢算唔算曠課 仲要咁嘅情緒 真係適合估老師？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"888d5c03062a6dee30b154cb0b5d7fc6de16f663","tid":2178641,"uid":290804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:31:11.000Z","msg":"真係適合做老師？"},{"pid":"9cfd2daba93ada0ad9351b3cacf3b226e18dedf6","tid":2178641,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:33:28.000Z","msg":"點解呀sir 唔話，我教書姐唔係rap,唔駛打拍子既，之後做個on9 動作扮下yo,全班笑完，咪繼續囉。<br />\n條友都on99"},{"pid":"0d2ee4639fe6fbb19c096bf4973aefd5d0c816a8","tid":2178641,"uid":132810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"有個女同學，一開學開始，成日冇端端大大聲鬧同學，次次嚇到我地呆咗。佢因為咁而RETAKE咗兩年。<br />\n<br />\n我地有時真係忍唔住，同班主任呀SIR投訴，點知佢叫我地反省下係未自己太小氣，同要學習容忍，由個女仔大聲鬧，唔理就得。<br />\n<br />\n最後，個女仔知呀SIR唔會鬧佢，所以學期尾，以買結婚禮物比MISS為由，呃哂全班錢。"},{"pid":"251161191ccef157347b0bdfbeb974dba9fe1e75","tid":2178641,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"樓主中文老師大問題啲喎<br />\n<br />\n霖乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357d59663c30064724b2360781f08cb4f840069c","tid":2178641,"uid":360082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:34.000Z","msg":"諗起小學教中文個miss又係好憎人玩原子筆，有次上堂我不自覺咁㩒咗幾下，佢即刻拍枱西面。不過佢以為係我斜前面個男仔，不停係到屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗起都覺得好對唔住個男仔。<br />\n但係個miss不嬲都好憎個男仔，可能佢只係借啲意屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e3db09f1b65416bea4d146e38846f6f43944b3","tid":2178641,"uid":290804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"251161191ccef157347b0bdfbeb974dba9fe1e75","tid":2178641,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"樓主中文老師大問題啲喎<br />\n<br />\n霖乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"Sor9 打開呢個字 有咩問題"},{"pid":"bfdd528a76ff81de648a5170825621a4a6b786e8","tid":2178641,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3e3db09f1b65416bea4d146e38846f6f43944b3","tid":2178641,"uid":290804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"251161191ccef157347b0bdfbeb974dba9fe1e75","tid":2178641,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"樓主中文老師大問題啲喎<br />\n<br />\n霖乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"Sor9 打開呢個字 有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔識字喺香港冇問題"},{"pid":"faa51a530627aeead6cb9a8be2c75eaab273c9f4","tid":2178641,"uid":290804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfdd528a76ff81de648a5170825621a4a6b786e8","tid":2178641,"uid":11506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3e3db09f1b65416bea4d146e38846f6f43944b3","tid":2178641,"uid":290804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"251161191ccef157347b0bdfbeb974dba9fe1e75","tid":2178641,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"樓主中文老師大問題啲喎<br />\n<br />\n霖乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:42:21.000Z","msg":"Sor9 打開呢個字 有咩問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔識字喺香港冇問題